OL,4,C'Hero plumber' has citizen award
OL,5,Crescinded
OL,6,GThe man once dubbed the country's
OL,7,G"kindest plumber" has had his British
OL,8,GCitizen Award rescinded following a
OL,9,GBBC investigation.
OL,11,FJames Anderson, from Burnley, was
OL,12,Fgiven the accolade in 2023 for his
OL,13,Fwork providing boilers and plumbing
OL,14,Fservices for free.
OL,16,FThe BBC revealed on Thursday that Mr
OL,17,FAnderson's firm, Depher, a social
OL,18,Fenterprise, faked stories of helping
OL,19,Fpeople as it raised millions in
OL,20,Fdonations.
